<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sports Zone: Your Ultimate Sports Event Hub</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #ff0000;
            --secondary: #000000;
            --background: #000000;
            --surface: #121212;
            --text-primary: #ffffff;
            --text-secondary: #888888;
            --gradient: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff0000, #800000);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--background);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .nav-container {
            background: var(--surface);
            border-bottom: 1px solid #333333;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            padding: 12px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 935px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .nav-content {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: var(--gradient);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
        }

        .nav-menu {
            display: flex;
            gap: 24px;
            list-style: none;
        }

        .nav-link {
            color: var(--text-primary);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: color 0.3s;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .nav-link:hover {
            color: var(--primary);
            background-color: rgba(255,0,0,0.1);
        }

        main {
            margin-top: 80px;
            padding: 40px 0;
        }

        .hero-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        .hero-title {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            background: var(--gradient);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: var(--surface);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
        }

        .feature-icon {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .feature-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .feature-description {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        .testimonials {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
        }

        .testimonial-card {
            background: var(--surface);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }

        .testimonial-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .testimonial-avatar {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 12px;
            background: var(--gradient);
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        footer {
            background: var(--gradient);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 0;
            margin-top: 60px;
        }

        .footer-content {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer-links {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 24px;
            margin-top: 16px;
        }

        .footer-link {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            opacity: 0.8;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
        }

        .footer-link:hover {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav-menu {
                gap: 16px;
            }

            .hero-title {
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            .hero-subtitle {
                font-size: 16px;
            }

            .features-grid,
            .testimonials {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .footer-links {
                flex-wrap: wrap;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="nav-container">
        <div class="container nav-content">
            <div class="logo">SportZone</div>
            <ul class="nav-menu">
                <li><a href="/" class="nav-link">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/about" class="nav-link">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="#features" class="nav-link">Features</a></li>
                <% if (user) { %>
                    <li><a href="/logout" class="nav-link">Logout</a></li>
                <% } else { %>
                    <li><a href="/login" class="nav-link">Login/Register</a></li>
                <% } %>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <div class="container">
            <section class="hero-section">
                <h1 class="hero-title">Sports Zone: Your Ultimate Sports Event Hub</h1>
                <p class="hero-subtitle">Unlock the full potential of your sports events with Sports Zone. Plan, manage, and engage with a community of sports enthusiasts.</p>
            </section>

            <section id="features" class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <svg class="feature-icon" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3M16 7V3M3 8h18M4 12h16m-1 8h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2v-5H9v5a2 2 0 01-2 2H5m10 0h2"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Event Planner</h3>
                    <p class="feature-description">Plan and organize your sports events with our intuitive event planner tool.</p>
                </div>
            
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <svg class="feature-icon" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 20h10m-5-16a2 2 0 110 4 2 2 0 010-4zM4 15a4 4 0 014-4h8a4 4 0 014 4v1H4v-1z"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Team Organizer</h3>
                    <p class="feature-description">Effortlessly create and manage your sports teams with our team organizer.</p>
                </div>
            
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <svg class="feature-icon" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 17a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4zM6.343 9.657a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4zM15.657 9.657a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4zM6.343 14.343a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4zM15.657 14.343a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Performance Analyzer</h3>
                    <p class="feature-description">Track and analyze detailed performance metrics for your teams and players.</p>
                </div>
            
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <svg class="feature-icon" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 11l7 7 7-7M3 5h18"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Ranking Tracker</h3>
                    <p class="feature-description">Stay updated with real-time rankings and leaderboards for various sports events.</p>
                </div>
            
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <svg class="feature-icon" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 7h10M7 11h10m-5 4h5M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Mobile Access</h3>
                    <p class="feature-description">Manage your sports events on the go with our mobile-friendly platform.</p>
                </div>
            
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <svg class="feature-icon" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5-5V4a3 3 0 00-5 5h-5v2m0 0h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5-5V4a3 3 0 00-5 5h-5v2m0 0h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5-5V4a3 3 0 00-5 5h-5v2"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Community Builder</h3>
                    <p class="feature-description">Connect with other sports enthusiasts and build a vibrant community around your favorite sports.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section id="testimonials" class="testimonials">
                <div class="testimonial-card">
                    <div class="testimonial-header">
                        <div class="testimonial-avatar">AB</div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold ml-2">Alex Brown</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">"SportZone has transformed the way we plan and execute our sports events. It's a game-changer!"</p>
                </div>
            
                <div class="testimonial-card">
                    <div class="testimonial-header">
                        <div class="testimonial-avatar">CL</div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold ml-2">Chris Lee</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">"The performance analyzer on SportZone provides deep insights that help us improve our game."</p>
                </div>
            
                <div class="testimonial-card">
                    <div class="testimonial-header">
                        <div class="testimonial-avatar">EM</div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold ml-2">Emma Martinez</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">"I love how SportZone keeps me connected with my sports community. It's more than just a platform; it's a community."</p>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="container footer-content">
                    <span>© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> SportZone™. All Rights Reserved.</span>
            <ul class="footer-links">
                <li><a href="/about" class="footer-link">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="/privacy-policy" class="footer-link">Privacy Policy</a></li>
                <li><a href="/licensing" class="footer-link">Licensing</a></li>
                <li><a href="/contact" class="footer-link">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
